#: resources/ui/setup.ui:10
msgid "Servers"
msgstr "Server"

#: resources/ui/setup.ui:19
msgid "Connect to Server"
msgstr "Connetti al Server"

#: resources/ui/setup.ui:20
msgid ""
"Gelly supports Jellyfin and Subsonic/Navidrome. Enter the full server URL "
"including protocol and port. For Jellyfin this is usually 8096, Navidrome "
"uses 4533."
msgstr ""
"Gelly supporta Jellyfin e Subsonic/Navidrome. Inserisci l'indirizzo completo "
"del server, inclusi protocollo e porta. Per Jellyfin quest'ultima è "
"solitamente 8096, Navidrome usa 4533."

